{"id":24648,"date":"2024-02-27T17:25:24","date_gmt":"2021-08-27T11:55:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=24648"},"modified":"2023-11-17T19:02:04","modified_gmt":"2023-11-17T13:32:04","slug":"straight-kitchen-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/straight-kitchen-design\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Minimalistic Modern Straight Kitchen Design Ideas You Must Consider"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Enjoy a hassle-free cooking experience in these straight modular kitchens<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Old but classic! Straight kitchens are back in trend. It is the ideal choice for urban dwellers living in tiny apartments or someone who enjoys minimalism. As the name suggests, this type of kitchen is made along a single wall. Here, a cooking hob, a refrigerator and a washbasin are linearly arranged on the countertop, making every item easily accessible and cooking much more convenient. Though it sounds all elementary, in reality, designing and building this type of straight kitchen while ensuring it\u2019s aesthetically attractive are exceptionally challenging. So, if you are looking for inspiration, here are some modern straight kitchen designs you must consider before deciding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Space-Saving Versatile Straight Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you live in a tiny apartment where you cannot afford to have a separate kitchen and lots of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-cabinet-storage-ideas\/\">storage cabinets<\/a>, this modular straight line kitchen design has to be your lifesaver. This olive-green-and-white-themed kitchen has every necessary amenities you can think of for an Indian household. It includes a side-by-side double door refrigerator, an OTG, a four-burner kitchen stove, a chimney, lots of sleek cabinets, hooks to hang ladles and cups and an ultra-smart space-saving wall-mounted dining table that also has secret storage inside. With innovative modular oil pull-out, lift-up shutters, clear <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/types-of-glass-kitchen-cabinets\/\">glass cabinets<\/a>, etc., you\u2019ll never run out of storage space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160446\/space-saving-versatile-straight-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"Straight kitchen design in olive green and white themed is a versatile space-saving kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-24649\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160446\/space-saving-versatile-straight-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160446\/space-saving-versatile-straight-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160446\/space-saving-versatile-straight-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160446\/space-saving-versatile-straight-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Choosing the proper storage for a modular straight kitchen is the ultimate test for interior designers<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"430\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-430x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Compact home with a straight modular kitchen design and it's advantages\" class=\"wp-image-51674\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-430x1024.jpg 430w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-126x300.jpg 126w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-768x1828.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-645x1536.jpg 645w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-860x2048.jpg 860w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes-150x357.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17185447\/advantage-of-straight-kitchen-in-compact-homes.jpg 941w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Be Playful Yet Strategic With The Colour Scheme<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A straight kitchen is excellent for smaller spaces. But since it\u2019s situated in an open area, it\u2019s essential to choose a suitable colour scheme so that it doesn\u2019t look like an eyesore. You can even experiment with pops of colours. For instance, the kitchen shown in the image has a contrasting colour scheme. With all the cabinets painted in black, the beige mosaic tiled backsplash and bright olive green countertop seem to breathe oxygen into the kitchen. Also, the glass crockery cabinet works perfectly as a showcase. You can also use it to store colourful containers and jars to add further colour. Additionally, the small space beside the kitchen has been used strategically as a dining table. Two overhead <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/hanging-kitchen-shelves-ideas\/\">hanging shelves<\/a> are also utilised to store items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160832\/straight-modular-kitchen-designs-with-colour-scheme.jpg\" alt=\"Straight modular kitchen designs with cabinets painted in black, the beige mosaic tiled backsplash\" class=\"wp-image-24651\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160832\/straight-modular-kitchen-designs-with-colour-scheme.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160832\/straight-modular-kitchen-designs-with-colour-scheme-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160832\/straight-modular-kitchen-designs-with-colour-scheme-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27160832\/straight-modular-kitchen-designs-with-colour-scheme-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Choosing the correct colour scheme for an open straight kitchen is tricky<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Modern Classic Straight Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The below image is the perfect example of how you can infuse classic charm into a modern modular straight kitchen design. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/white-kitchen-cabinet-ideas\/\">white wooden cabinets<\/a> are giving the kitchen a vintage vibe when the structure is modern. It has it all \u2014 a large <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-pantry-cabinet\/\">pantry cabinet<\/a>, an oven, a four-burner hob, a sink, a refrigerator and numerous storage cabinets \u2014 below and above the countertop and even one above the fridge. The glass cabinet in between is made to break the monotony. The kitchen flaunts a butcher block countertop to match the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dining-room-interiors\/modern-wooden-dining-table-designs\/\">wooden dining table<\/a>. It is lit by overhead lights. The backlight underneath the top cabinet creates an ambience that highlights the brick-like backsplash.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27161242\/modern-straight-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern straight kitchen design with white wooden cabinets and large pantry cabinet\" class=\"wp-image-24653\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27161242\/modern-straight-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27161242\/modern-straight-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27161242\/modern-straight-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27161242\/modern-straight-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bring old-world charm into your modern straight kitchen design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Design yourself a clever space saving kitchen\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/09124831\/design-yourself-clever-space-saving-kitchen.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-arch-design\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kitchen Arch Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Ultra Small Straight Kitchen For Studio Apartments<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you live in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/studio-apartment-interior-design-ideas\/\">compact studio apartment<\/a>, this small straight kitchen design is perfect for you. Built-in a minimal wall space, this kitchen has enough storage space to hold crockery, utensils, cutlery and grocery for more than two people. Though the design doesn\u2019t include a refrigerator, it compensates with a small sink, an oven, a sleek chimney, and an induction cooktop. In this straight kitchen design, even dead spaces like that over the chimney, under the sink and under base units are well utilised with vertical lift-up shutter, under-sink unit and skirting drawer. Follow this design if you also live in a small space like this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27162838\/the-ultra-small-straight-line-kitchen-design-studio-apartments.jpg\" alt=\"The studio apartments' ultra-small straight line kitchen design features enough storage space to hold crockery\" class=\"wp-image-24670\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27162838\/the-ultra-small-straight-line-kitchen-design-studio-apartments.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27162838\/the-ultra-small-straight-line-kitchen-design-studio-apartments-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27162838\/the-ultra-small-straight-line-kitchen-design-studio-apartments-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27162838\/the-ultra-small-straight-line-kitchen-design-studio-apartments-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Maximise space with compact straight kitchen design for small studio apartments<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Straight Kitchen Design With Island<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/indian-style-kitchen-interior-designs\/\">Indian kitchen<\/a>, islands aren\u2019t commonly used. But it is advantageous if you enjoy multifunctionality. Islands become the architectural focal point of your kitchen while giving you plenty of space for meal preparation, storage and eating when you don\u2019t have time for elaborate dining. It also is a great hangout spot when you have your friends over, especially if you add a few high stools and stylish looking pendant lights, like shown in the image below. You can install a sink and drawers at the bottom to create additional storage space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27163106\/straight-line-modular-kitchen-designs-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"Straight line modular kitchen design with island with high stools and stylish looking pendant lights\" class=\"wp-image-24672\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27163106\/straight-line-modular-kitchen-designs-with-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27163106\/straight-line-modular-kitchen-designs-with-island-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27163106\/straight-line-modular-kitchen-designs-with-island-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/27163106\/straight-line-modular-kitchen-designs-with-island-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make islands a centre of attraction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you have found your inspiration for giving your kitchen a makeover of a lifetime from these designs. However, if you have some queries, we are here to help you clear them all. Book a consultation today and get your questions answered directly from our team of expert <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">interior designers<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you liked reading about modern straight kitchen designs, also have a look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.de